        "TileImage": "$($repository 1e5f8f18-029a-4ef5-be4c-9874e34b0b4c).Image",
        "Description": "As the Delgado drug cartel grows in power, it has become more and more important to secure as many possible ports along the southern and eastern seaboards in order to keep profit up to match rising operational costs.\r\rThe less powerful Santos cartel still retains a marginal hold on the cocaine trafficking to Miami, mostly due to their man on the ground, lieutenant Alex Moyer, doubling as the head of Krontstadt security.\r\rTake Moyer out, and convince the Santos cartel to skip town.",
